NAME
    App::nodie - runs immortal processes

VERSION
    version 1.00

SYNOPSIS
            #!/bin/sh
            perl -MApp::nodie -erun -- command arg1 arg2 ...

DESCRIPTION
    App::nodie runs immortal processes.

    See also: nodie.pl
    <https://metacpan.org/pod/distribution/App-Virtualenv/lib/App/nodie/nodi
    e.pl>

INSTALLATION
    To install this module type the following

            perl Makefile.PL
            make
            make test
            make install

    from CPAN

            cpan -i App::nodie

DEPENDENCIES
    This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    *   Scalar::Util

    *   Lazy::Utils

REPOSITORY
    GitHub <https://github.com/orkunkaraduman/App-nodie>

    CPAN <https://metacpan.org/release/App-nodie>

